Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:05.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bring you marvelous illusions that \Nmake this town sparkle at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:12.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy the miracle that is going \Nto happen under the moonlight tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This isn't it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:27.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one I gotta return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:48.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:50.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic tricks and magic spells \Ncan both be considered "magic,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:03.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:14.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know there's \Nno such thing as {\i1}real{\i0} magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirror, mirror, on the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:33.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who's the fairest of them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:37.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be you, Akako-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:41.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men all over the world are enamored of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:46.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Except for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? And who might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:54.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:02.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid the Phantom Thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:47.99,Signs - Thief Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)}Scarlet Seduction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:47.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaito, don't you want something sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. For instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoko, have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgotten what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back when I had that cavity...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:06.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that bulging cheek! \NWhat a weird face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You laughed! So you think I'm \Ngonna fall for it now, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's February 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All girls bring chocolate to school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:23.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the day when we give it to boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:27.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure nobody else \Nwould give you any,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:32.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only giving it to you \Nbecause I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's a romantic \Nfull moon out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it snows, we'll have \Na white Valentine's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.22,0:04:41.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Keiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:46.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun ran off thataway with \Na big grin plastered on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:50.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna give that \Nchocolate to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:51.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You vixen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:53.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who would give that guy chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky to have someone \Nto give it to, Aoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:03.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is monopolizing all the other guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:10.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi Akako, who just \Nstarted here a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:15.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akako-sama, give me chocolate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She acts like she's royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Akako-chan really is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:37.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single man in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:41.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is wrapped around my little finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all the loot I got!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:47.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's from Misaki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's from Sakura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is from Ayano-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:57.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aoko, why is everyone \Ngiving me chocolate today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:59.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was saying, today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:02.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I never \Ncome to school on February 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:05.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, I had a terrible cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The year before, I was hospitalized with \Na broken ankle after a skating accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:16.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought it was an unlucky day, \Nnever knowing what I was missin' out on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Akako-chan! Give me chocolate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one of Kaito's tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:40.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want my chocolate, you'll \Nhave to dump all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You're \Nbeing rude to Akako-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:50.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:54.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't {\i1}need{\i0} my chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:04.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's like snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone, take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you brought chocolate too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for you, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of {\i1}course{\i0} you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:28.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid the Phantom Thief is the \Nonly one who can resist me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless {\i1}he's{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aoko, have you seen my hankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't seen your stupid hankie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me borrow you a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:54.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rotten to the core!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll expose your other identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything ready for the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:38.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is all set, Akako-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:49.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get over how ugly you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:55.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And you are always \Nbeautiful, Akako-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:09:01.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the rightful heir to red magic. You \Nshould become the empress of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:05.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! I'm tired of hearing you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I shall begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:15.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon's whisker, mermaid's tear, \Neyeball of a {\i1}kappa{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:23.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I give you this handkerchief, \Nsymbolizing Kuroba Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:37.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall soon be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:40.51,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Parrot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:47.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess February 14th is an \Nunlucky day for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, \Nit's been a sweet day for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, I've got \Na feeling of foreboding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope I don't get injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.09,0:10:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:06.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:10.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe in real magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:16.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Real" magic does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:22.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Another term for it would be "sorcery."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:26.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Different kinds of sorcery \Nhave color designations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:30.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are black magic, white magic,\N blue magic, red magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Red magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:36.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorcerers are the mortal \Nenemies of us magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:40.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been at odds with each other \Nsince ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:47.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of them despise us, and \Nconsider what we do "fake magic."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Despise us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:54.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, there's \Na full moon tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:58.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's long been said that the full moon \Nis an omen of bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, please watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I sent out advance notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for one of the \Noldest tricks in the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Knockout gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Find him! He can't have gone far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who fall for old tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is no good... I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:11.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool. Did you really \Nthink you could get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:23.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me, Kid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, Kuroba Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Grab him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:33.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll release you from your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So come to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:08.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bad feeling about tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry. I'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that, Jii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not our enemies tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to me, Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly... You're almost here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who the hell you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but at least your night flight woke me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you from your torments.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:59.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, \Nmy ostentatious rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:06.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, {\i1}you're{\i0} going to be the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:11.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I'm going to steal your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch cold in that outfit, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you supposed to be a gentleman now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, hand over that doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:36.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:45.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... red magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this would finally be \Nthe year I could give it to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,God's mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body already belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, become my servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you sure are a spoiled young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:59.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Again, become my servant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:11.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid. You want to escape \Nthat agony, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:15.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then eat this chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:18.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:26.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This time you'll accept my red feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although after receiving it,\N your heart will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...mine for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:41.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, your magic \Ndoesn't work on me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:52.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow put out my magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:12.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,White Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the magic of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the trick up your sleeve, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:27.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You always use magic tricks to \Nescape when you're in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:30.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, they're all a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They just fool people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is real! The effects really happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:42.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to escape?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:52.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, the magic I perform fools people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:55.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone who sees it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:08.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They enjoy being fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:11.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the difference between \Nyour magic and mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:19.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealing people's hearts \Nthrough sorcery is just sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:25.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that's how we witches operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's telling lies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:38.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, you are. You're lying to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, you can't fool \NKid the Phantom Thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:50.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see the beautiful gem lying \Ndeep within your frozen heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Akako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:59.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, cute sorceress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:16.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. If a witch sheds a tear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:19.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll lose her magic power forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have that chocolate \Nfrom yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That only means something if \NI give it out on Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This is the chocolate from...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:06.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not the same one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:11.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroba Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a sorceress and magician, we share the \Nbond of knowing each other's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:25.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I {\i1}will{\i0} make you mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:30.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:31.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:34.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Akako-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:42.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:50.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's meet again \Nunder the falling snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:53.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See you next illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm usually at the top of my game \Nwhen it comes to thieving and magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:35.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but once in a while, \Nthings don't go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This town has had a clock tower \Nfor many years now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and my target is the \Ndiamond-encrusted hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:43.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but somebody's seeing through \Nmy every move?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely not old man Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:48.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.57,0:23:53.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:53.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Magic Kaito 1412{\i0}:\N Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:56.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Step right this way! Watch carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:58.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the illusion!
